<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
<title>百炼计划 - 成长中心</title>
<link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>🦞</text></svg>">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
:root{--red:#E63946;--red-dark:#C1121F;--red-light:#FF6B6B;--gold:#D4A843;--gold-light:#F0D78C;--bg:#F5F0EB;--bg-card:#FFFFFF;--text:#1A1A2E;--text-light:#666680;--text-lighter:#999;--shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);--radius:12px;--radius-sm:8px;}
body{font-family:-apple-system,"PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;}
input,button,select,textarea{font-family:inherit;font-size:inherit;}
#loginScreen{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--red),var(--red-dark));display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;z-index:1000;}
#loginScreen .logo{text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;}
#loginScreen .logo .icon{width:80px;height:80px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 16px;font-size:40px;}
#loginScreen .logo h1{color:#fff;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;}
#loginScreen .logo p{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-size:14px;margin-top:4px;}
#loginScreen .card{background:#fff;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:32px 24px;width:100%;max-width:360px;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);}
#loginScreen .card label{display:block;font-size:14px;color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:6px;}
#loginScreen .card input{width:100%;padding:14px 16px;border:2px solid #eee;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:18px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;}
#loginScreen .card input:focus{border-color:var(--red);}
#loginScreen .card .btn{width:100%;padding:14px;background:var(--red);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;margin-top:16px;transition:background .2s;}
#loginScreen .card .btn:hover{background:var(--red-dark);}
#loginScreen .card .error{color:var(--red);font-size:13px;margin-top:8px;display:none;}
#loginScreen .card .hint{text-align:center;color:var(--text-lighter);font-size:13px;margin-top:12px;}
#app{display:none;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;min-height:100vh;background:var(--bg);position:relative;}
.topBar{background:var(--red);color:#fff;padding:12px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
.topBar .userInfo{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1.3;}
.topBar .userInfo .name{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;}
.topBar .userInfo .id{font-size:12px;opacity:0.8;}
.topBar .actions{display:flex;gap:12px;}
.topBar .actions button{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border:none;color:#fff;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;font-size:18px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:background .2s;}
.topBar .actions button:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);}
#content{padding:16px 16px 80px;overflow-y:auto;}
.tabBar{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);max-width:480px;width:100%;background:#fff;border-top:1px solid #eee;display:flex;z-index:100;padding:4px 0;padding-bottom:max(4px,env(safe-area-inset-bottom));}
.tabBar .tab{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:6px 0;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-lighter);font-size:11px;transition:color .2s;border:none;background:none;}
.tabBar .tab .tab-icon{font-size:22px;line-height:1.2;}
.tabBar .tab.active{color:var(--red);font-weight:600;}
.page{display:none;}
.page.active{display:block;}
.homeHero{text-align:center;padding:16px 0;}
.homeHero .lobsterWrap{width:200px;height:240px;margin:0 auto 12px;position:relative;}
.homeHero .levelBadge{display:inline-block;background:var(--red);color:#fff;padding:4px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;}
.homeHero .levelName{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;}
.homeHero .levelName .lv{color:var(--red);}
.homeHero .gpText{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:12px;}
.homeHero .gpText strong{color:var(--text);font-size:18px;}
.progressCard{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:16px;}
.progressCard .label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:4px;}
.progressCard .barWrap{background:#eee;border-radius:10px;height:14px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;}
.progressCard .barFill{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red-light),var(--red));height:100%;border-radius:10px;transition:width .5s ease;}
.progressCard .barText{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-lighter);margin-top:4px;text-align:right;}
.progressCard .nextInfo{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:8px;}
.quickLinks{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.quickLinks a{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:14px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text);box-shadow:var(--shadow);transition:transform .15s;}
.quickLinks a .ql-icon{font-size:28px;display:block;margin-bottom:4px;}
.quickLinks a .ql-label{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;}
.quickLinks a .ql-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-lighter);}
.announcements{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:12px 16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
.announcements .title{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.announcements .item{padding:6px 0;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);border-bottom:1px solid #f5f5f5;}
.announcements .item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.recordsList{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden;}
.recordsList .record{padding:12px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f5f5;}
.recordsList .record .r-left{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
.recordsList .record .r-date{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-lighter);}
.recordsList .record .r-source{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;}
.recordsList .record .r-points{color:var(--red);font-weight:700;font-size:16px;}
.recordsList .empty{text-align:center;padding:32px;color:var(--text-lighter);font-size:14px;}
.mapLevels{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;position:relative;padding-left:40px;}
.mapLevels::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:18px;top:0;bottom:0;width:3px;background:#eee;border-radius:2px;}
.mapLevel{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px;position:relative;margin-bottom:4px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);transition:all .2s;}
.mapLevel::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:-28px;top:20px;width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:#eee;border:3px solid var(--bg);z-index:1;}
.mapLevel.current{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff5f5,#fff);border:2px solid var(--red);}
.mapLevel.current::before{background:var(--red);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(230,57,70,0.2);}
.mapLevel.reached{opacity:0.85;}
.mapLevel.reached::before{background:var(--red-light);}
.mapLevel .ml-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:4px;}
.mapLevel .ml-head .ml-lv{font-size:13px;color:var(--red);font-weight:700;}
.mapLevel .ml-head .ml-name{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;}
.mapLevel .ml-head .ml-badge{font-size:11px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px;background:#eee;}
.mapLevel .ml-head .ml-badge.current-badge{background:var(--red);color:#fff;}
.mapLevel .ml-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);}
.mapLevel .ml-gp{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-lighter);margin-top:4px;}
.rewardsSection{margin-bottom:16px;}
.rewardsSection .sectionTitle{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.rewardsGrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:10px;}
.rewardCard{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
.rewardCard .rc-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;flex-shrink:0;}
.rewardCard .rc-icon.unclaimed{background:#fff5f5;}
.rewardCard .rc-icon.claimed{background:#f0f0f0;}
.rewardCard .rc-icon.locked{background:#f5f5f5;}
.rewardCard .rc-body{flex:1;}
.rewardCard .rc-body .rc-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;}
.rewardCard .rc-body .rc-condition{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-lighter);margin-top:2px;}
.rewardCard .rc-btn{padding:8px 16px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;}
.rewardCard .rc-btn.unclaimed{background:var(--red);color:#fff;}
.rewardCard .rc-btn.claimed{background:#eee;color:var(--text-lighter);cursor:default;}
.rewardCard .rc-btn.locked{background:#f5f5f5;color:#ccc;cursor:default;}
.lbTabs{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px;}
.lbTabs .lbt{flex:1;padding:10px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;background:#eee;color:var(--text-light);}
.lbTabs .lbt.active{background:var(--red);color:#fff;}
.lbList{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden;}
.lbEntry{display:flex;align-items:center;padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f5f5;}
.lbEntry .lb-rank{width:28px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.lbEntry .lb-rank.gold{color:var(--gold);}
.lbEntry .lb-rank.silver{color:#aaa;}
.lbEntry .lb-rank.bronze{color:#cd7f32;}
.lbEntry .lb-name{flex:1;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;margin:0 12px;}
.lbEntry .lb-points{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--red);}
.lbEmpty{padding:32px;text-align:center;color:var(--text-lighter);font-size:14px;}
.learnCard{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;}
.learnCard .lc-icon{width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:28px;flex-shrink:0;}
.learnCard .lc-icon.yixue{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff5f5,#ffe0e0);}
.learnCard .lc-icon.caijing{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f4fd,#d0eafc);}
.learnCard .lc-icon.special{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff8e1,#ffecb3);}
.learnCard .lc-icon.activity{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fce4ec,#f8bbd0);}
.learnCard .lc-body{flex:1;}
.learnCard .lc-body .lc-title{font-size:17px;font-weight:600;}
.learnCard .lc-body .lc-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:2px;}
.learnCard .lc-btn{background:var(--red);color:#fff;padding:10px 20px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;text-decoration:none;}
#adminPanel{display:none;padding:16px 16px 80px;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;min-height:100vh;background:var(--bg);}
#adminPanel .adminHeader{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px;}
#adminPanel .adminHeader h2{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;}
#adminPanel .adminHeader button{background:#eee;border:none;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;}
#adminPanel textarea{width:100%;height:180px;border:2px solid #ddd;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);padding:12px;font-size:13px;font-family:monospace;resize:vertical;outline:none;}
#adminPanel textarea:focus{border-color:var(--red);}
#adminPanel .adminBtns{display:flex;gap:10px;margin:12px 0;}
#adminPanel .adminBtns button{flex:1;padding:12px;border:none;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;}
#adminPanel .adminBtns .btn-import{background:var(--red);color:#fff;}
#adminPanel .adminBtns .btn-export{background:var(--gold);color:#fff;}
#adminPanel .adminStatus{padding:10px 12px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:13px;margin:8px 0;display:none;}
#adminPanel .adminStatus.success{background:#d4edda;color:#155724;display:block;}
#adminPanel .adminStatus.error{background:#f8d7da;color:#721c24;display:block;}
#adminPanel .adminPreview{overflow-x:auto;}
#adminPanel .adminPreview table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;}
#adminPanel .adminPreview th,#adminPanel .adminPreview td{border:1px solid #ddd;padding:6px 8px;text-align:left;}
#adminPanel .adminPreview th{background:#f5f5f5;font-weight:600;position:sticky;top:0;}
.snackbar{position:fixed;bottom:80px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:#333;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;z-index:9999;display:none;animation:fadeIn .3s;}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}}
@media(min-width:480px){#app,.tabBar,#adminPanel{max-width:480px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;}}

.ptCard{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:12px;}
.ptHeader{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.ptIcon{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;}
.ptIcon.yixue{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff5f5,#ffe0e0);}
.ptIcon.caijing{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f4fd,#d0eafc);}
.ptTitle{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;}
.ptTag{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-lighter);background:#f5f5f5;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:8px;}
.ptRow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f5f5;}
.ptRow:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.ptCheck{width:20px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;}
.ptLabel{flex:1;font-size:14px;}
.ptPoints{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--red);}
.ptMax{padding:10px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);}
.ptTotal{border-left:4px solid var(--gold);}
.ptTotalRow{font-size:14px;padding:4px 0;}
.ptDelay{border-left:4px solid var(--red);background:#fff8f8;}
.ptDelayBody{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.7;}
.ptLevels{border-left:4px solid #74B9FF;}
.ptLvRow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f5f5;font-size:14px;}
.ptLvRow:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.ptLvBadge{display:inline-block;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:8px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0;width:36px;text-align:center;}
.ptLvBadge.lv1{background:#999;}
.ptLvBadge.lv2{background:#74B9FF;}
.ptLvBadge.lv3{background:#4A90D9;}
.ptLvBadge.lv4{background:#E63946;}
.ptLvBadge.lv5{background:#D4A843;}
.ptLvBadge.lv6{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D4A843,#FFD700);}
.ptLvBadge.lv7{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#E63946,#FFD700);}
.ptLvGp{color:var(--text-lighter);font-size:12px;margin-left:auto;}

/* Lobster animations */
@keyframes lobsterIdle{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(-1deg)}25%{transform:translateY(-3px) rotate(1deg)}50%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(-1deg)}75%{transform:translateY(-4px) rotate(2deg)}}
@keyframes lobsterBounce{0%{transform:scale(1) translateY(0)}15%{transform:scale(1.1) translateY(-14px)}30%{transform:scale(0.95)}50%{transform:scale(1.08) translateY(-6px)}80%{transform:scale(0.98)}100%{transform:scale(1) translateY(0)}}
.lobsterBounce{animation:lobsterBounce 0.5s ease-out !important}


/* My ranking */
.myRank{background:var(--bg-card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:14px 16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin-bottom:12px;display:none;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
.myRank .mrIcon{font-size:30px;flex-shrink:0;}
.myRank .mrBody{flex:1;}
.myRank .mrRank{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--red);line-height:1.2;}
.myRank .mrDesc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);}
.myRank .mrPoints{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);}
.myRank .mrLabel{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-lighter);margin-bottom:2px;}


/* Aircraft Carousel */
.aircraft-wrap{position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:100%;height:220px;}
.aircraft-svg{flex:1;height:180px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;cursor:pointer;}
.aircraft-svg svg{max-width:160px;max-height:140px;}
.aircraft-btn{position:absolute;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:32px;height:32px;border:none;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);color:#666;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;z-index:5;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.aircraft-btn:hover{background:#fff;color:#E63946;}
.aircraft-btn.l{left:0;}
.aircraft-btn.r{right:0;}
.aircraft-info{text-align:center;padding:6px 0 4px;}
.aircraft-info .ac-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;}
.aircraft-info .ac-name .lock{font-size:12px;color:#bbb;}
.aircraft-dots{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:6px;padding:4px 0;}
.aircraft-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;}
.aircraft-dot.active{background:#E63946;transform:scale(1.3);}
.aircraft-dot.unlocked{background:#aaa;}
.aircraft-dot.locked{background:#eee;}
50%{box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,215,0,0.8);transform:scale(1.1)}}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="loginScreen">
<div class="logo"><div class="icon">🦞</div><h1>百炼计划</h1><p>成长中心</p></div>
<div class="card">
<label for="memberId">请输入您的精网号</label>
<input type="text" id="memberId" placeholder="例如：JH0001" autocomplete="off">
<div class="error" id="loginError">未找到该精网号，请确认后重试</div>
<button class="btn" id="loginBtn">进入成长中心</button>
<div class="hint">联系客服获取您的精网号</div>
</div></div>
<div id="app">
<div class="topBar"><div class="userInfo"><span class="name" id="userName">-</span><span class="id" id="userId">精网号: -</span></div><div class="actions"><button id="adminBtn" title="管理后台">⚙</button></div></div>
<div id="content">
<div class="page active" id="pageHome">
<div class="homeHero"><div class="lobsterWrap" id="lobsterDisplay"></div><div class="levelBadge" id="levelBadge">LV1</div><div class="levelName"><span class="lv" id="lvName">龙虾学徒</span></div><div class="gpText">成长值 <strong id="gpCount">0</strong></div></div>
<div class="progressCard"><div class="label">成长进度</div><div class="barWrap"><div class="barFill" id="progressBar" style="width:0%"></div></div><div class="nextInfo"><span id="nextLevelText">距离下一等级：30成长值</span><span id="progressPercent">0%</span></div></div>

<div class="quickLinks"></div>
<div class="announcements"><div class="title">📢 公告</div><div id="announcementList"></div></div>
</div>
<div class="page" id="pageRecords">
<h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;">成长记录</h3>
<div class="recordsList" id="recordsList"></div>
</div>
<div class="page" id="pageMap">
<h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;">成长地图</h3>
<div class="mapLevels" id="mapLevels"></div>
</div>
<div class="page" id="pageRewards">
<h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;">奖励中心</h3>
<div class="rewardsSection"><div class="sectionTitle">🎁 可领取奖励</div><div class="rewardsGrid" id="rewardsUnclaimed"></div></div>
<div class="rewardsSection"><div class="sectionTitle">✅ 已领取奖励</div><div class="rewardsGrid" id="rewardsClaimed"></div></div>
<div class="rewardsSection"><div class="sectionTitle">🔒 未解锁奖励</div><div class="rewardsGrid" id="rewardsLocked"></div></div>
</div>
<div class="page" id="pageLeaderboard">
<h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;">荣誉榜</h3>
<div id="myRankDisplay" class="myRank">
<div class="mrIcon">🏆</div>
<div class="mrBody">
<div class="mrLabel">我的排名</div>
<div class="mrRank">#1</div>
<div class="mrDesc">共 0 人</div>
</div>
<div class="mrPoints">0 成长值</div>
</div>
<div class="lbTabs"><button class="lbt active" data-lb="weekly">本周</button><button class="lbt" data-lb="monthly">本月</button><button class="lbt" data-lb="cumulative">累计</button></div>
<div class="lbList" id="lbList"></div>
</div>
<div class="page" id="pageLearn">
<h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;">积分获取说明</h3>
<div class="ptCard"><div class="ptHeader"><span class="ptIcon yixue">📺</span><span class="ptTitle">易学久会</span><span class="ptTag">软件实操训练营</span></div><div class="ptRow"><span class="ptCheck">✅</span><span class="ptLabel">进入直播间签到</span><span class="ptPoints">+1</span></div><div class="ptRow"><span class="ptCheck">✅</span><span class="ptLabel">观看时长≥20分钟</span><span class="ptPoints">+1</span></div><div class="ptRow"><span class="ptCheck">✅</span><span class="ptLabel">参与课堂互动</span><span class="ptPoints">+1</span></div><div class="ptMax"><span class="ptCheck">📌</span>每日上限 <strong>3</strong> 成长值</div></div><div class="ptCard"><div class="ptHeader"><span class="ptIcon caijing">📈</span><span class="ptTitle">财经壹眼</span><span class="ptTag">市场认知提升</span></div><div class="ptRow"><span class="ptCheck">✅</span><span class="ptLabel">进入直播间签到</span><span class="ptPoints">+1</span></div><div class="ptRow"><span class="ptCheck">✅</span><span class="ptLabel">观看时长≥20分钟</span><span class="ptPoints">+1</span></div><div class="ptRow"><span class="ptCheck">✅</span><span class="ptLabel">参与课堂互动</span><span class="ptPoints">+1</span></div><div class="ptMax"><span class="ptCheck">📌</span>每日上限 <strong>3</strong> 成长值</div></div><div class="ptCard ptTotal"><div class="ptHeader"><span class="ptIcon">📋</span><span class="ptTitle">每日合计</span></div><div class="ptTotalRow">两个栏目每日最多可获 <strong>6</strong> 成长值</div></div><div class="ptCard ptDelay"><div class="ptHeader"><span class="ptIcon">⏰</span><span class="ptTitle">到账说明</span></div><div class="ptDelayBody">成长值在直播结束后不会立即到账。<br>运营人员将在每日直播结束后统一统计并导入数据。<br>一般在 <strong>次日可查看</strong> 最新成长值。<br><br>如有疑问请联系客服。</div></div><div class="ptCard ptLevels"><div class="ptHeader"><span class="ptIcon">🗺️</span><span class="ptTitle">等级一览</span></div><div class="ptLvRow"><span class="ptLvBadge lv1">LV1</span>龙虾学徒 <span class="ptLvGp">0-29</span></div><div class="ptLvRow"><span class="ptLvBadge lv2">LV2</span>龙虾侦察兵 <span class="ptLvGp">30-59</span></div><div class="ptLvRow"><span class="ptLvBadge lv3">LV3</span>龙虾先锋 <span class="ptLvGp">60-119</span></div><div class="ptLvRow"><span class="ptLvBadge lv4">LV4</span>龙虾领队 <span class="ptLvGp">120-179</span></div><div class="ptLvRow"><span class="ptLvBadge lv5">LV5</span>龙虾舰长 <span class="ptLvGp">180-359</span></div><div class="ptLvRow"><span class="ptLvBadge lv6">LV6</span>荣誉舰长 <span class="ptLvGp">360-719</span></div><div class="ptLvRow"><span class="ptLvBadge lv7">LV7</span>传奇领航官 <span class="ptLvGp">720+</span></div></div></div>
